1.text: Place a square sheet of origami paper with the colored side face down.

2.text: Fold the paper in half from top to bottom.

3.text: Fold the rectangle in half again to form a square and then unfold it.

4.text: Fold both sides toward the central crease to form quarters.

5.text: Open the upper left flap and press it into a triangle.

6.text: Repeat this process with the upper right flap of the paper.

7.text: Flip over the paper to view your finished origami house.

8.text: Place the house upright to display it.
